- **TOOL-022 (new, P2)** — Hyphenated node IDs from Figma URLs (`2010-73`) are rejected; the API wants colon form (`2010:73`). `use_file` tolerates the URL form but `read`/`edit`/`screenshot` don't, so reusing the same ID stumbles once. Fix: normalize `^(\d+)-(\d+)$` → `$1:$2` at the tool boundary.
